<table class="table">
  <thead>
  <tr>
    <th width="20%">商品名称</th>
    <th width="15%">采购目录</th>
    <th width="7%">小计数量</th>
    <th width="10%">小计金额（元）</th>
    <th width="10%">未关联数量</th>
    <th width="10%">未关联金额（元）</th>
    <th width="8%">状态</th>
    <th width="20%">关联计划书</th>
  </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  {{#each data}}
    {{#each items}}
      <tr data-item="{{json this}}" data-sku-id="{{sku.id}}">
        <td>{{itemName}}</td>
        <td class="js-item-catalog" data-catalog="{{json catalogNodes}}"></td>
        <td>{{itemCount}}</td>
        <td class="js-purchase-money" data-price="{{sku.price}}" data-count="{{itemCount}}"></td>
        <td>{{unbindCount}}</td>
        <td class="js-purchase-unbind-money" data-price="{{sku.price}}" data-count="{{unbindCount}}"></td>
        <td class="js-bind-status" data-count="{{itemCount}}" data-remain="{{unbindCount}}"></td>
        <td class="js-bind-plans" data-plans="{{json plans}}">
          {{#each plans}}
            <div class="purchase-plan-box js-purchase-plan-item" data-plan="{{json this}}" data-pop="">
              <div class="purchase-plan-no">
                <a class="js-open-purchaseplan" href="javascript:void(0)" data-id="{{confirmationId}}">{{confirmationName}}</a>
              </div>
              <button class="btn btn-small btn-info js-modify-purchase-plan-item">修改关联</button>
              <button class="btn btn-small btn-info js-cancel-purchase-plan-item">取消关联</button>
            </div>
          {{/each}}
        </td>
      </tr>
    {{/each}}
  {{else}}
    <tr><td colspan="8" class="text-center">没有商品信息</td></tr>
  {{/each}}
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="bottom-tips">
  <p>
    限定资产目录：商品所属采购目录必须与计划书采购目录完全相同<br>
    非限定资产目录：商品所属采购目录的父级二级目录必须是计划书内采购目录的父级（例：二级目录A09办公消耗用品及类似物品，三级目录A0901纸制文具及办公用品，三级目录A0902 硒鼓、粉盒，如果申请了A0902，即可购买A0901的商品）
  </p>
</div>